{"word":"H2550 - חָמַל - châmal - khaw-mal' - Have compassion","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">חָמַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>châmal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>khaw-mal'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Have compassion"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தப்பவை, தலையசை, சேர், இரங்கு, கடாட்சி, தயைவை, இரக்கமுள்ளதாயிரு. இரக்கமாயிரு, இரங்கங்கொள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"(Qal) to spare, to pity, to have compassion on"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>commiserate</i>; by implication to <i>spare: - </i>have compassion, (have) pity, spare."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2538 - חָמוּל - Châmûwl - khaw-mool'/2538\">H2538</a>, <a href=\"#/H2539 - חָמוּלִי - Châmûwlîy - khaw-moo-lee'/2539\">H2539</a>, <a href=\"#/H2550 - חָמַל - châmal - khaw-mal'/2550\">H2550</a>, <a href=\"#/H2551 - חֶמְלָה - chemlâh - khem-law'/2551\">H2551</a>, <a href=\"#/H4263 - מַחְמָל - machmâl - makh-mawl'/4263\">H4263</a>"}]}